  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Indexed\n63\n28\n\n7) is not God + is in process of self completion as the highest entity/being/organism in the world (Arius) 8) while totally rational + wise, + implants/imparts this to world, does not have personality -as God does- + does not possess agapē as its einai; noein is its einai (2-3-74 + 11-17-80). 9) The world order (i.e. reality / the universe / creation) is being assimilated by it (Teilhard de Chardin). Viz: it originally acted as the agent of creation (since it preceeded creation), ",
      "matched_alias": "Chardin",
      "term_id": "TERM_chardin",
      "term_name": "Chardin",
      "term_slug": "chardin"
    }
